msgstr "使用这个主题来帮助您通过 Windows PowerShell 管理 Windows 和 Windows Server 技术。"

msgid "# Stop-VM"
msgstr "# 停止虚拟机"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Shuts down, turns off, or saves a virtual machine."
msgstr "关闭、终止或保存虚拟机。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "### Name (Default)"
msgstr "### 名称（默认值）"

msgid "### VMObject"
msgstr "### VMObject"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Stop-VM** cmdlet shuts down, turns off, or saves a virtual machine."
msgstr "**Stop-VM** cmdlet 用于关闭、断开连接或保存虚拟机。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1"
msgstr "### 示例 1"

msgid "Shuts down virtual machine TestVM through the guest operating system."
msgstr "通过客户机操作系统关闭虚拟机TestVM。"

msgid "### Example 2"
msgstr "### 示例 2"

msgid ""
"Shuts down virtual machine TestVM through the guest operating system, regardless of any unsaved application data.\n"
"Hyper-V gives the guest five minutes to save data, then forces a shutdown.\n"
"This shutdown can result in loss of unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"通过客户机操作系统关闭虚拟机TestVM，无论其中是否有未保存的应用程序数据。Hyper-"
"V会给客户机五分钟的时间来保存数据，之后强制关闭该虚拟机。这种关闭操作可能会导致未保存的数据丢失。"

msgid "### Example 3"
msgstr "### 示例 3"

msgid ""
"Turns off virtual machine TestVM.\n"
"This operation is equivalent to disconnecting the power from the virtual machine, and can result in loss of unsaved data."
msgstr "关闭虚拟机 TestVM。此操作相当于切断该虚拟机的电源供应，可能会导致未保存的数据丢失。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid "Runs the cmdlet as a background job."
msgstr "以后台作业的形式运行该cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer.\n"
"Enter a computer name or a session object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967) or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet.\n"
"The default is the current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该cmdlet。可以输入一个计算机名称，或者一个会话对象（例如 `[New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)` 或 `[Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966)` cmdlet "
"的输出结果）。默认值是本地计算机上的当前会话。"

msgid ""
"Specifies one or more Hyper-V hosts on which a virtual machine is to be shut down.\n"
"NetBIOS names, IP addresses, and fully qualified domain names are allowable.\n"
"The default is the local computer.\n"
"Use localhost or a dot (.) to specify the local computer explicitly."
msgstr ""
"指定一个或多个用于关闭虚拟机的 Hyper-V 主机。可以使用 NetBIOS 名称、IP 地址或完全限定的域名进行选择。默认值为本地计算机。可以使用 "
"`localhost` 或`.` 明确表示本地计算机。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行该cmdlet之前，会提示您进行确认。"

msgid ""
"Specifies one or more user accounts that have permission to perform this action.\n"
"The default is the current user."
msgstr "指定一个或多个具有执行此操作权限的用户账户。默认值为当前用户。"

msgid ""
"Specifies that the shutdown of the virtual machine is to be forced.\n"
"If the virtual machine has applications with unsaved data, the virtual machine has five minutes to save data and shut down.\n"
"If the virtual machine is locked, it is shut down immediately."
msgstr ""
"指定必须强制关闭虚拟机。如果该虚拟机上运行有未保存数据的应用程序，系统会给予该应用程序五分钟的时间来保存数据并完成关闭操作；如果虚拟机处于锁定状态，则会立即将其关闭。"

msgid "Specifies the name of the virtual machine to be shut down."
msgstr "指定要关闭的虚拟机的名称。"

msgid ""
"Specifies that a **Microsoft.HyperV.PowerShell.VirtualMachine** object is to"
" be passed through to the pipeline representing the virtual machine to be "
"shut down."
msgstr ""
"指定要将一个 **Microsoft.HyperV.PowerShellvirtualMachine** 对象传递给管道，该对象代表需要关闭的虚拟机。"

msgid "Specifies that the virtual machine is to be saved."
msgstr "指定要保存该虚拟机。"

msgid "Specifies that the virtual machine is to be turned off."
msgstr "指定要关闭该虚拟机。"

msgid "Specifies the virtual machine to be shut down."
msgstr "指定要关闭的虚拟机。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上这个cmdlet并没有被运行。"

